            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>tomatoes</strong> finely</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Zest 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1]</span> <strong>lime</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Roll the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p>",
